snippet.title: The Butterfly Dreams - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming September 2nd, 2024 on itch.io
https://avenueq.itch.io/the-butterfly-dreams
A group of seven distinguished luminaries from various fields have gathered.
They're there to create whole worlds, whole universes indistinguishable from the real world, limited only by their imagination.

Who are they, and what dreams will they dream?
